<div class="page-hero">
  {% render 'breadcrumb', breadcrumb_title: 'Privacy Policy' %}
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>How we collect, use, and protect your personal information</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="policy-content">

    <div class="policy-block fade-in">
      <div class="policy-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you place an order or create an account on our website, we collect personal information such as your name, email address, mailing address, phone number, and payment information necessary to complete your purchase.</p>
        <p>We also collect information you voluntarily provide, such as when you contact us through our contact form or subscribe to our newsletter.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block fade-in">
      <div class="policy-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:2;padding-left:20px;margin-top:8px;">
          <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
          <li>Send order confirmations and shipping updates</li>
          <li>Respond to your questions and support requests</li>
          <li>Improve our products and services</li>
          <li>Send promotional communications (only if you opt in)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block fade-in">
      <div class="policy-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Information Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information. Our website is hosted on Shopify, which provides industry-standard security measures including SSL encryption for all transactions.</p>
        <p>We never store your full credit card number — all payment processing is handled securely through Shopify's certified payment partners.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block fade-in">
      <div class="policy-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use Shopify to power our online store. You can review Shopify's privacy policy at <a href="https://www.shopify.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:600;">shopify.com/legal/privacy</a>.</p>
        <p>We may use third-party services such as Google Analytics to help us understand how customers use our site. These services have their own privacy policies and may collect information as described in those policies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block fade-in">
      <div class="policy-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please contact us:</p>
        <p><strong>Rejoice Dance Ministry</strong><br>
        2479 West 80 Street, Hialeah, Florida 33016<br>
        Phone: <a href="tel:+13055582212" style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:600;">305-558-2212</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-cta fade-in">
      <p>Questions about your data or your order?</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-top:20px;">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="{{ pages['contact'].url }}">Contact Us</a>
        <a class="btn-secondary" href="{{ routes.collections_url }}">Shop Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
.policy-block {
  display: flex;
  gap: 28px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 40px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.policy-block:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
.policy-icon {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 60px; height: 60px;
  background: var(--purple-pale);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  color: var(--purple);
}
.policy-block h2 {
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--purple-dark); margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.policy-block p {
  color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.85;
  margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.97rem;
}
.policy-cta {
  text-align: center; margin-top: 60px;
  padding: 48px;
  background: var(--purple-pale);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.policy-cta p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1rem; }
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .policy-block { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
}
</style>
